headline: Bank of America Partners with Sir David Beckham as it Expands its Global Sports Partnerships
summary: Today, Bank of America announced a multi-year partnership with global sports leader, entrepreneur and philanthropist, Sir David Beckham, to be an ambassador for its global sports program, Sports with Us. The partnership will see Sir David promote the bank's full sports partnership portfolio, which includes iconic brands and events to drive progress, celebrate achievement and support communities.
